1 Week Ago However, as the second week of April winds down, Mohammed said the timeframe extends to Saturday.  While addressing State House correspondents on Wednesday, the minister also said there is “no big issue” yet regarding Buhari’s expected return.  “Today is Wednesday; this week finishes on Saturday. So, what is the big issue in that one?” the minister asked.